# 🔐 SecureOps SOC Platform

A Security Operations Center (SOC) simulation platform designed to demonstrate core cybersecurity operations including incident management, threat intelligence, vulnerability management, MITRE ATT&CK mapping, security reporting, and SIEM-style detection workflows.

Built as a portfolio project to showcase practical cybersecurity concepts and SOC analyst skills.

---

## 📌 Overview

SecureOps SOC Platform is a browser-based cybersecurity dashboard that simulates the workflow of a modern Security Operations Center.

The platform allows users to:

* Monitor security incidents
* Investigate threats
* Track Indicators of Compromise (IOCs)
* Manage vulnerabilities
* Map attacker techniques using MITRE ATT&CK
* Generate security reports
* Review audit logs
* Simulate SIEM detection pipelines

The goal of this project is to demonstrate understanding of cybersecurity operations and incident response processes in a practical environment.

