### ⚡ Detection Pipeline (SIEM Simulation)

One of the core features of the platform.

The Detection Pipeline demonstrates how a SOC processes security events from detection to response.

Workflow:

```text
Windows Event Logs
        ↓
Detection Rules
        ↓
Alert Correlation
        ↓
MITRE ATT&CK Mapping
        ↓
Incident Creation
        ↓
Analyst Investigation
```

Simulated Detection Rules:

* Failed Logins (Event ID 4625)
* Privileged Logins (4672)
* PowerShell Abuse (4104)
* Audit Log Clearing (1102)
* Ransomware Activity
* Office Process Execution

